snippet.title: The Sad Truth About Angelina Jolie's Transgender Son
snippet.description:
The Dark Truth About Angelina Jolie's Transgender Son

Shiloh Nouvel Jolie-Pitt, the first biological child of Angelina Jolie and Brad Pitt, recently stepped out looking much different from her usual tomboy self.
When Shiloh was just 2 years old, Angelina revealed that Shiloh wants to be a boy and for years, we’ve gotten used to seeing Shiloh wearing boy’s clothes and rocking a boyish haircut.
But these days, Shiloh is looking very much different from what we’re used to and it seems like her tomboyish style was just a phase.
So what’s really going on with Shiloh, and why is her gender identity making headlines?

#angelinajolie #bradpitt #shilohjolie
